Invocation Name: compare food
des: Ever wondered how handy it will be if you could compare macro nutrients of "Wheat and Rice" or "Tomato and Potato" or even "Apple and Orange"? This tool does exactly that. Just call out any two food items to compare. If bored just say "Compare any two foods" for random pick up
